<recipe lang="en-uk" xmlns:lxslt="http://xml.apache.org/xslt">
<title><![CDATA[Parsnip soup with fried apples]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[The sweetness of the fried apples combines wonderfully with the spicy parsnips in this easy soup. Serves four.]]></description>
<source/>
